data.description: Introducing this darling one-level home, nestled in a charming neighborhood of Parkrose. This residence is perfectly suited for individuals looking to downsize or first-time home buyers, offering a cozy and low-maintenance living space. With fresh new paint both inside and out, new cabinets and appliances, this home is move-in ready! The open and airy layout of this home maximizes the use of space, creating a comfortable living area that invites relaxation or entertainment. The one-level convenience ensures easy access to every room, catering to those seeking a simple and effortless daily lifestyle. Step outside to the backyard where you'll find a fresh expanse of new grass, providing a green canvas for your outdoor aspirations. This blank slate presents the perfect opportunity to design your ideal outdoor space, maybe a tranquil garden or an inviting patio space, or both!Located by a myriad of amenities, take advantage of the local parks, schools, and shopping centers. Additionally, the convenient access to major highways ensures convenient commuting and easy exploration of the surrounding areas.This small yet thoughtfully remodeled home is an excellent choice for buyers looking to downsize or enter the real estate market for the first time. Its low-maintenance design, fresh updates, and convenient location make it an attractive opportunity not to be missed.
